Class FullCommandNameTree

  • java.lang.Object
    • clishell.FullCommandNameTree

  • public class FullCommandNameTree
extends java.lang.Object
    Class to manages multi-word "command names" as tree of words. Examples of "command names" include:
    • help
    • set color
    • set style
    • load static file from
